RequestBody.name: JS SDK Test Assistant - Nickname
RequestBody.instructions:
You are a helpful assistant. Use the provided functions to help answer questions.
              Customize your responses to the user's preferences as much as possible and use friendly
              nicknames for cities whenever possible.

function.name: getUserFavoriteCity
function.description: Gets the user's favorite city.

function.name: getCityNickname
function.description: Gets the nickname for a city, e.g. 'LA' for 'Los Angeles, CA'.

city.description: The city and state, e.g. San Francisco, CA
